{"tid":1658720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[10.20］極重要共識！唔該入黎","createTime":"2019-10-16T14:56:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T00:29:38.000Z","uid":84396,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"845600b5fa52713cd066eef60cf793cdfeafe287","tid":1658720,"uid":84396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:56:17.000Z","msg":"呢個時候爆單南亞人襲擊岑子杰 一定有好多陰謀<br />\n<br />\n但有啲基本共識我地一定要有 唔可以比佢煽動到<br />\n<br />\n預左比人屌中計撚<br />\n<br />\n大家都知好多南亞人係手足黎<br />\n<br />\n係太子見過 係金鐘見過 連電台訪問都有南亞手足<br />\n（睇live）<br />\n<br />\n所以有鑑於星期日遊行路線經過地點，希望各位有以下共識：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咪撚攪重慶大廈同清真寺</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我武斷啲講句 到時邊到主動提出/行動裝修以上地點<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全部都係鬼</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n香港人還拖！<br />\n<br />\n10.20 尖沙咀見</span></span>"},{"pid":"34c7247f8b06a62013097419fabeac60ab7e495c","tid":1658720,"uid":84396,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:56:23.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"8dbf9d658f483a3d3c179b0b3df641152d4ae180","tid":1658720,"uid":84396,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:56:37.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"d07e1a0e7c54a94e4badc1dbd590d81f5124d205","tid":1658720,"uid":84396,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:56:48.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"128cbe05088d3fa21e7f1b837d4b9ba65e8e266b","tid":1658720,"uid":84396,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:57:03.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"2811c002b7537939e016208120e4d11bb78cc373","tid":1658720,"uid":84396,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:57:13.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"d765c4b0bf5331a6408312b51ecd4f1f9bb2b897","tid":1658720,"uid":84396,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16